│ possibility of producing a poison value when   │
│ the operands are not of the same sign. This    │
│ behavior is not currently accounted for in the │
│ transformation logic, leading to the incorrect │
│ optimization observed in the reproducer.       │
│                                                │
│ ### Diagnosis and Fix Plan:                    │
│                                                │
