│ a poison value if the operands are not of the  │
│ same sign.                                     │
│    - The transformation in                     │
│ `foldAndOrOfICmpsWithConstEq` does not         │
│ consider this behavior, leading to an          │
│ incorrect optimization where the resulting IR  │
│ is more poisonous than the original.           │
│                                                │
│ 2. **Analyzing `opt`'s Log**:                  │
│    - The transformation replaces the `select`  │
│ instruction with the `icmp samesign`           │
