│ transformation if the `icmp` instruction uses  │
│ the `samesign` predicate.                      │
│                                                │
│ 5. **Conclusion**:                             │
│    - The fix ensures that the transformation   │
│ logic respects the poison semantics of the     │
│ `icmp samesign` instruction.                   │
│    - This prevents the introduction of         │
│ incorrect optimizations that result in more    │
